>>>>>>> # Diabetes Research Steering Group: Acute Care
>>>>>>> ### The Acute Care group will focus on the urgent in-hospital care
that people with diabetes need and receive. This group will cover urgent in-
hospital care, including - but not limited to - severe hypoglycaemia, diabetic
>>>>>>> It will also cover in-patient care for people with diabetes and its
